          <para>There are two ways to draw on this surface: by overriding the <see cref="M:SkiaSharp.Views.Mac.SKGLView.DrawInSurface" /> method, or by attaching a handler to the <see cref="E:SkiaSharp.Views.Mac.SKGLView.PaintSurface" /> event.</para>
